==發行==
特別版[[DVD|DVD]]附有一本32頁的圖像小說''[[Hard_Choices_'What_happened_on_Algol?'|Hard Choices 'What happened on Algol?']]''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultramarinesthemovie.com/shop |title=Special Edition DVD and graphic novel details on Official site |publisher=Ultramarinesthemovie.com |date= |accessdate=2011-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110214010738/http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/shop |archive-date=2011-02-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，該書由[[Dan_Abnett|Dan Abnett]]撰寫，並由知名的漫畫書藝術家[[David_Roach|David Roach]]插畫，特別版預定在2010年11月29日在世界各地發行。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/shop |title=Official site DVD release information |publisher=Ultramarinesthemovie.com |date= |accessdate=2011-02-16 |archive-date=2020-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220065044/http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/shop |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，根據Codex Pictures 在2010年11月29日的聲明，因為一個生產上的問題，DVD的發行延遲了。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/news/2010-11-29/delay-ship-date |title=Delay To Ship Date |publisher=Ultramarines the movie |date=2010-11-29 |accessdate=2011-02-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101184611/http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/news/2010-11-29/delay-ship-date |archivedate=2011-01-01 }}</ref>該問題的詳細內容並未公布，不過Codex Pictures聲名說這問題和DVD無關，而是和典藏版DVD的一項物品有關。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/news/2010-12-01/ultramarines-delivery-update |title=Ultramarines delivery update |publisher=Ultramarines the movie |date= |accessdate=2011-02-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101225193323/http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/news/2010-12-01/ultramarines-delivery-update |archivedate=2010-12-25 }}</ref>

Codex Pictures之後宣佈該影片會在12月6日星期一上市，而且他們將優先處理影片的發行，依照他們收到訂單的日期把貨送到顧客那裡，最後一份在該周的週末送出。然而，這並未解決所有問題，有許多人早在10月就下了訂單，至2011年1月27日卻仍未收到他們的貨品。這件事又被Codex Pictures的網站仍在販賣的DVD混淆的更深，並且他們沒有清楚地警告前述媒體的供應是有問題的。 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/news/2010-12-03/important-news-about-delivery |title=Important news about delivery |publisher=Ultramarines the movie |date= |accessdate=2011-02-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101228160032/http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/news/2010-12-03/important-news-about-delivery |archivedate=2010-12-28 }}</ref>

==評價==
《極限戰士》預先的放映由一小群選定的觀眾給出了不錯的回應。然而，這部片的CGI和動畫被一些人認為有點廉價的味道：CGI讓極限戰士們看起來「高」而「瘦」，同時不少影片的場景是由灰塵掩蓋的；最大的不滿則是，考量到戰鎚美術包含的細節和創意以後，這部片看起來很廉價、製作的匆忙、而且簡單。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ultramarinesthemovie.com/blog/2010-11-19/first-reactions-ultramarines-movie |title=First Reactions to Ultramarines movie |publisher=Ultramarinesthemovie.com |date= |accessdate=2011-02-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101228170844/http://www.ultramarinesthemovie.com/blog/2010-11-19/first-reactions-ultramarines-movie |archivedate=2010-12-28 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dakkadakka.com/wiki/en/yakface_Reviews_the_Ultramarines_Movie |title=Articles — yakface Reviews the Ultramarines Movie |publisher=DakkaDakka |date=2007-09-19 |accessdate=2011-02-16 |archive-date=2020-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201091706/https://www.dakkadakka.com/wiki/en/yakface_Reviews_the_Ultramarines_Movie |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="aintitcool.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/47565 |title=Massawyrm enjoys the hell out of the Warhammer 40,000 CG feature film ULTRAMARINES [Ain't It Cool News] |publisher=Aintitcool.com |date= |accessdate=2011-02-16 |archive-date=2017-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002184402/https://www.aintitcool.com/node/47565 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

也有些人認為故事劇情過於簡單，進展緩慢，並缺乏神祕感和重要感。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dakkadakka.com/wiki/en/yakface_Reviews_the_Ultramarines_Movie#The_Story |title=Articles — yakface Reviews the Ultramarines Movie |publisher=DakkaDakka |date=2007-09-19 |accessdate=2011-02-16 |archive-date=2020-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201091706/https://www.dakkadakka.com/wiki/en/yakface_Reviews_the_Ultramarines_Movie#The_Story |dead-url=no }}</ref>影片對於視覺性細節的注重也被提到，例如在背景的每片彩色玻璃都有他們的故事。<ref name="aintitcool.com"/>影片在[[IMDB|IMDB]]上使用者平均評分為5.8/10。<ref name="#1"/>

